divs: Sighting Detailsstanding outside the firehouse talking with the guys. we looked up and saw this light that looked like it was shining down like a large flashlight. way to high to be a helicopter or plane. it satied in place but kinda moved back and forth. then some clouds or smoke started to cover the light. the "smoke" became thicker until the light disappeared. there were no othert clouds in the sky. we tried to debug this but could not. this was seen by 5 firefighters.
